/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Destiny in Play</span><hr size=1> Raven had been in her hut for what seemed to be weeks. Yakut and Tanna were married and Dakor was gone  . . . . for now.<br><br>She eventually rose from her scrolls and walked over to the door where she opened it looking at Terasi.<br><br>&quot;What's wrong Terasi? Is my mother well?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 137<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/18/02 1:08:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tribal Matters</span><hr size=1> &lt;Terasi&gt; <br>Terasi bowed to Raven.<br><br>&quot;Queen Yakut is fine, but she wishes to speak with you concerning Tribal matters.&quot;<br><br>She then stood waiting to be dismissed by the Prigkipissa.<br><br>&lt;Yakut&gt;<br><br>Yakut waited.......<br><br>&lt;Rae&gt;<br><br>&quot;Princess Lynn?&quot;<br><br>She knocked again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uprincesslynn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Princess Lynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/18/02 9:28:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tribal Matters</span><hr size=1> Lynn was laying down on her bed. She kinda ignored the first knocks, but not wondered who would be knocking at her door. Feeling she wasnt importent enough to be visited. So Lynn got up and opened her door. &quot;Yes?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/19/02 3:10:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tribal Concerns?</span><hr size=1> Raven quirked a brow and walked to her dresser grabbing her leather overcoat seeing it was a rather chilly night. She followed Terasi out the door and over to the Queen's hut. She waited outside until she would be summoned in by her Mother the Queen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/19/02 5:08:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Queen</span><hr size=1> &lt;Terasi&gt;<br><br>Walks into the Hut.<br><br>&quot;She awaits your calling Vasilissa.&quot;<br><br>Terasi walked outside giving the Queen her time qith Raven.<br><br>&lt;Yakut&gt;<br><br>She nodded.<br><br>&quot;My Kouri, Enter.&quot;<br><br>Yakut pulled off her shaman headdress and laid it in her lap.<br><br>&lt;Rae&gt;<br><br>&quot;Princess Lynn, The Queen wishes to speak with you on Tribal Matters, please report to her immediatly.&quot;<br><br>Rae saluted Lynn then walked away into her own hut. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/20/02 2:03:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmm</span><hr size=1> Raven nodded to Terasi and walked into the hut where she gave a respectful nod to her mother. She quirked a brow at her Mother's odd form and questioned her.<br><br>&quot;Mother, what is going on? Is something happening with the tribe?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 142<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/20/02 4:31:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A New Sunset</span><hr size=1> &quot;Yes, Raven something is happening.&quot;<br><br>Yakut took in a deep breath.<br><br>&quot;On the Night of the Full Moon, my time as Queen will have set like the sun. On the Very next day, The sun will rise and with it a new Queen and Queen's Rite of Caste.&quot;<br><br>Yakut stood and hung her headdress on the wall.<br><br>&quot;I am resigning as Queen, giving you and Lynn the tribe. Together you shall rule Tanais River Valley. You will share the responsibilties and wars together. Though I hope this tribe stays in peace but when you are Queen, it will be up to you.&quot;<br><br>She waited Raven's re-action to the news. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/23/02 3:05:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> What?</span><hr size=1> She blinked a few times hearing this news. <br><br>&quot;What? I . .  I mean . . . Mother the traditions are that when a Queen leaves her lands and departs for another home, she resigns her position.&quot;<br><br>The tradition usually spoke of when a Queen died and left her lands to go to the Amazon Lands of the Dead. But technically Raven didn't know that Yakut was leaving Tanias Valley and moving to Scynthia. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 146<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/24/02 1:52:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> &quot;Well, I am doing so in accordance with Amazon Law. I am moving to Scynthia with Tanna, Glory and Ariel.&quot;<br><br>Yakut knew her time here was done. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/25/02 1:25:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> But. . .</span><hr size=1> Raven still felt a bit odd about this whole thing. If Yakut was leaving with Tanna and Ariel, that left Raven and her sister.<br><br>&quot;But I don't understand . . . who is to be Queen then?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 149<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/25/02 4:37:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/yakut.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Raven</span><hr size=1> &quot;You are. Lynn will be moved up to your Rite of Caste. Ariel and Glory will still be the Princesses but until thery are older will lodge with me. Lynn is in much the same position as Prigkpissa Del. With a few exceptions of course.&quot;<br><br>Yakut wondered....<br><br>&quot;Do you not accept this great honor I have offered you? My decision disappoints you?&quot;<br><br>Yakut had to move on from TRV. She loved this place with all her heart but a calling had came to her. <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§ <BR>~Northern Amazon Queen of Tanais River Valley~<BR>"An Eye for an Eye just makes the whole World blind."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amazonprincessraven>Amazon Princess Raven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/27/02 3:15:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Honor</span><hr size=1> Raven stood tall and rose her head. She then bowed her head before her Mother.<br><br>&quot;I do accept this rite for I have been preparing for it my entire life. I will not dishonor you mother.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 154<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(3/27/02 6:08:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Strength and Honor</span><hr size=1> Yakut smiled.<br><br>&quot;At the next full moon, you shall rise as the Queen of Tanais River Valley. Fron now and everyday foreward you are to act as Queen.&quot;<br><br>The Ceremony and Celebration was already being planned. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showPrevMessage?topicID=32.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showNextMessage?topicID=32.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=32.topic&index=13><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/rust/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.emailToFriend?topicID=32.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.threadControl?topicID=32.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/rust/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=32.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm29.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=32.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm35">Amazon 